 

 

GENDER PAY GAP REPORT 
 

Openwork is required by law to publish an annual gender pay gap report. 

This is its report for the snapshot date of 5 April 2017. 

•  The mean gender pay gap for Openwork is 37.28%. 
•  The median gender pay gap for Openwork is 18.62%. 
•  The mean gender bonus gap for Openwork is 69.83%. 
•  The median gender bonus gap for Openwork 33.30%. 
•  The proportion of male employees in Openwork receiving a bonus is 73.53% and the proportion of 

female employees receiving a bonus is 79.14%. 

